sub_fields.label: Featured Posts
sub_fields.name: featured_posts
sub_fields.instructions: Featured posts allow you to select specific Posts or Events to display in the Latest News Carousel; if none are selected, the latest 4 news posts will be displayed by default.

sub_fields.label: Alignment
sub_fields.name: alignment

sub_fields.label: Allow Multiple Open Accordions
sub_fields.name: allow_multiple
sub_fields.instructions: Controls whether multiple accordion sections can be open simultaneously.
